il filmer om 2. verdenskrig i Europa i nyere tid."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "kultur"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "kultur|film"}, {"field": "category2", "value": "kultur|film|filmanmeldelser"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4e1887d4ae0786f2e8d18a243c8c33bdd208ce578a881e95b77e7448e4616a93"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-03-03T19:18:49.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "FILM: \u00abLore\u00bb er en original og eminent krigsfilm. Fem s\u00f8sken med naziforeldre pr\u00f8ver \u00e5 ta seg til slektninger nord i landet under Nazi-Tysklands sammenbrudd."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article8795147.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Lorebild.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/f2f80bdc45939ca7595f42e22db368aace6e8129.jpg?58b9c199"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Barnas undergang -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "f2f80bdc45939ca7595f42e22db368aace6e8129"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["trondheim kino", "kino", "dvd", "video", "kosmorama", "filmfestivaler"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "trondheim kino,kino,dvd,video,kosmorama,filmfestivaler"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["kultur", "filmanmeldelser", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["barnas undergang", "film"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["sommersault", "der untergang", "hitlerjugend", "lore", "nazi-tysklands", "cate shortland"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["europa", "tyskland"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "adolf hitlers"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["kultur/film/filmanmeldelser", "kultur", "kultur/film"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/kultur/article8795147.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Lorebild.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb